Name:                parse-dimacs
Version:             1.2
Cabal-Version:       >= 1.2
Synopsis:            DIMACS CNF parser library
Description:         

    A DIMACS CNF parser library, implemented with Parsec 3, using ByteStrings.
    DIMACS CNF is a file format for describing constraint problems in
    conjunctive normal form.

